$compound.execute: echo '$compound' | get_relationship_ParticipatesAs -to id | get_relationship_IsInvolvedIn -to id,name  | cut -f 3,4 | sort -u

$model.execute: echo '$model' | get_relationship_IsDividedInto -to id  | get_relationship_IsInstanceOf -to id  | get_relationship_IsParticipatingAt -to id | get_relationship_IsParticipationOf -to id

$feature.execute: query_entity_Feature -is 'source_id,$feature' | get_relationship_IsOwnedBy -to id | get_relationship_WasSubmittedBy -to id | grep -i 'seed' | cut -f1

$otu.execute: echo '$otu' | get_relationship_IsCollectedInto -to id | otus_to_representatives | get_entity_Genome -f scientific_name

$genome.execute: echo '$genome' | get_relationship_IsModeledBy -to id | get_relationship_HasRequirementOf -to id | get_relationship_IsExecutionOf -to id
